MODULE: adapters
FILES: 1
RESPONSIBILITY: External CLI adapter for invoking CodeBuddy process and streaming/collecting outputs
KEY_FILES:
- src/adapters/codebuddy.js: spawn wrapper with timeout, heartbeat logging, stdio echo, and failure normalization
INTERFACES:
- runCodeBuddy(prompt, options?): Promise<string>
DEPENDENCIES:
- node:child_process spawn: external command execution
- src/config.js: binary path, timeout, permission flag, echo settings
- src/utils/logger.js: lifecycle and heartbeat logging
